# LAMMPS Input File
# Licensed under CC BY 4.0
# A Set of Materials-Science Tutorials for the LAMMPS Simulation Package: 2. Materials Science
# By Simon Gravelle, Mark A. Tschopp, Jacob R. Gissinger, and Axel Kohlmeyer
# Tutorial 1: 1. Single point energy calculation

# 1) Initialization
units metal
dimension 3
boundary p p p
atom_style atomic

# 2) System definition
lattice fcc 4.049
region box block 0 4 0 4 0 4
create_box 1 box
create_atoms 1 box

# 3) Settings
pair_style eam/alloy
pair_coeff * * Al_zhou.eam.alloy Al

compute eng all pe/atom
compute eatoms all reduce sum c_eng

# 4) Monitoring
compute eng all pe/atom
compute eatoms all reduce sum c_eng
thermo 10
thermo_style custom step pe c_eatoms press lx ly lz

# 5) Run
run 0 post no
